§ Matrix notation ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Let $u_1 …, u_k ∈ 𝗥^n$. ⦉

  ‖ Define $U ∈ 𝗥^{n × k}$ so that
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ U = \bmat{u_1 ❲&❳ u_2 ❲&❳ ⋯ ❲&❳ u_k}. ⦉
    ⦉⦉

  ‖ Then $\set{u_1, …, u_k}$ is an orthonormal set mean
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ U^⊤U = I_k ⦉
    ⦉

    ‖ Notice that if $k < n$, $UU^⊤ ≠ I$, since its rank is
      at most $k$. ⦉⦉
⦉

